v>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/3azF3PN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GinglaBambino]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Weird trauma triggers</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NKF2WfJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8lPadFL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ok not literally allergic but pretty close — it turns out the normal sound of a baby crying is triggering some deep buried trauma and I end up having extreme panic attacks.
My husband and I have been trying to have a baby for 5 years and we now have an adorable 5 month old son. But I am a wreck. Took forever to figure it out (ruled out postpartum, etc) and apparently certain childhood traumas (I was abandoned by a mentally ill mother) get triggered by parenthood.
I am getting lots of help and support but I still feel… frustrated by the irony of it all.
#mentalhealth #mental_illness #parenting #life</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NKF2WfJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[betabot001]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>&quot;Always has been&quot; meme teed up and ready to fly!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8iqaEFr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hoXDdM7.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>(originally posted by @JayAdan on 2023-08-23 13:21:33)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8iqaEFr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThisTimeLastYear]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Teefs!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UhJTvmN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/K3UUJKA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Chomp!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UhJTvmN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[103Brewer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Me</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/n35PuRj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/l4EkZrj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/n35PuRj</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ultraruben]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's my cakeday enjoy, a dancing nun and Billy Jigsaw</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/yTwLHxF</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xQd19rr.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yTwLHxF</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SarahTheCuteVixen]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I got to build Legos for work</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/fOmj8rZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ofqo6Wp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TcXfhCS.jpg" style=